name: BabyBroccoli
description: BabyBroccoli ($BABYBROCCOLI) is a crypto memecoin that has emerged as the playful, 'baby' version of the $Broccoli token, inspired by Changpeng Zhao (CZ)'s dog named Broccoli, which he officially announced on X. Positioned as a community-driven project on the BNB Chain, $BABYBROCCOLI rewards its holders with official $Broccoli tokens.
